   getLogger().lifecycle(\"No matching coordinates found. Nothing to do.\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/CoordinatesAwareTask.java:60:            String coordinateFilter = Objects.toString(getProject().findProperty(\"coordinates\"), \"\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/AbstractLibraryStatsTask.java:59:        Object property = getProject().findProperty(\"coordinates\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/AbstractLibraryStatsTask.java:83:            throw new GradleException(\"No matching coordinates found for library stats generation.\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/AbstractSubprojectTask.java:116:        if (System.getenv(\"GVM_TCK_LV\") == null) {\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/AbstractSubprojectTask.java:118:            env.put(\"GVM_TCK_LV\", version);\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/SplitTestOnlyMetadataTask.java:46:            getLogger().lifecycle(\"No matching coordinates found for splitTestOnlyMetadata. Nothing to do.\");\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/SingleCoordinateTask.java:25:            throw new GradleException(\"No matching coordinates found. Provide a concrete coordinate via -Pcoordinates=group:artifact:version\");\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
